```

## BASE Layer (from keymap.yaml)
Row 0: `       Q       W       E       R       T       Y       U       I       O       P       -
Row 1: CAPS_W  A/GUI   S/ALT   D/CTRL  F/SHFT  G       H       J/SHFT  K/CTRL  L/ALT   ;/GUI   '
Row 2: C-s     Z       X       C       V       B       N       M       ,       .       /       none
Thumb:                 ESC/MED SPC/SYM TAB             RET     BSPC/NUM DEL/FUN

## Key Translations
- `&kp GRAVE` for backtick
- `&caps_word` for Caps Word
- `&kp LC(S)` for Ctrl+S (tmux prefix)
- `&hm LGUI A` for home-row mod
- `&lt MEDIA ESC` for layer-tap

## Layers
- BASE (0): QWERTY + home-row mods (GACS/SCAG)
- NUM (1): Numbers in numpad layout, hold BSPC
- SYM (2): Coding symbols, hold SPACE
- FUN (3): F-keys + arrows, hold DEL
- MEDIA (4): Media + BT, hold ESC

## Home-row mods
Left: A=GUI, S=ALT, D=CTRL, F=SHIFT
Right: J=SHIFT, K=CTRL, L=ALT, ;=GUI

## Behavior
```c
hm: homerow_mod {
    compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
    flavor = "balanced";
    tapping-term-ms = <200>;
    quick-tap-ms = <175>;
    bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
};
```

## SYM Layer (from keymap.yaml)
Purpose: Coding symbols optimized for Python/TypeScript

Row 0: none    ,       <       >       -       |       ^       {       }       $       →       none
Row 1: none    !       *       /       =       &       #       (       )       ;       "       none
Row 2: none    ~       +       [       ]       %       @       :       `       .       none    none
Thumb:                 (held)  trans   trans           trans   trans   trans

## Arrow Macro (→ key)
Outputs `->` on tap, `=>` when shift is held.

```c
macros {
    arrow: arrow {
        compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
        #binding-cells = <0>;
        wait-ms = <30>;
        tap-ms = <30>;
        bindings = <&kp MINUS &kp GT>;
    };
    fat_arrow: fat_arrow {
        compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
        #binding-cells = <0>;
        wait-ms = <30>;
        tap-ms = <30>;
        bindings = <&kp EQUAL &kp GT>;
    };
};

behaviors {
    arrow_morph: arrow_morph {
        compatible = "zmk,behavior-mod-morph";
        #binding-cells = <0>;
        bindings = <&arrow>, <&fat_arrow>;
        mods = <(MOD_LSFT|MOD_RSFT)>;
    };
};
```

## Key Translations
- `&kp LT` for <
- `&kp GT` for >
- `&kp PIPE` for |
- `&kp CARET` for ^
- `&kp LBRC` for {
- `&kp RBRC` for }
- `&kp DLLR` for $
- `&arrow_morph` for → position
- `&kp EXCL` for !
- `&kp ASTRK` for *
- `&kp FSLH` for /
- `&kp AMPS` for &
- `&kp HASH` for #
- `&kp LPAR` / `&kp RPAR` for ( )
- `&kp DQT` for "
- `&kp TILDE` for ~
- `&kp PLUS` for +
- `&kp PRCNT` for %
- `&kp AT` for @
- `&kp COLON` for :
